#3000
Near the Melee Magthere~
You are near the center of the cavern within which Valsharan Che'el exists.
To the south, you see a large square dominated by a statue of the Spider
Queen. To the north you can see the gates of the Melee Magthere. Although
the gates almost always stand open, it is rumored that in dire emergencies
the masters of the Magthere will order them closed.
~
