#3001
Before the Gates of the Melee Magthere~
Encircled in wreathing faerie fire, the gates of the Melee Magthere stand
open before you. Magthere itself seems to reach almost to the top of
the cavern and is covered with carvings of battles long forgotten and
weaponmasters long past. The gates themselves bare the image of a great
spider, who, perhaps if the gates would close would come to life to stand
guard over the Magthere.
