#3003
Lil Colbauth Oloth~
You are wandering the path of darkness within the glory that is Valsharan,
first city of the underdark. Although the drow of other cities would claim
otherwise, the elders claim that Valsharan was founded during the first
years of the drow coming to the underdark. No drow now living remembers
those events, and Lloth is, as always, silent about such matters, but it
is, to the drow of Valsharan, a matter of honor that their city shall 
always remain great in the eyes of outsiders.
~
