#3018
Near the Northern Gate~
You are at the inner gate of Valshara. To the north of you, the path continues
to the guard towers and the outer gate. If Valshara were to be invaded, both
gates would be closed, as would the entrances to the towers, making the
city almost inpregnable. To the south, the cavern glows brightly in the light
of purple faerie fire and the distant spires of the northern noble houses
can be seen clearly.
~
