#3019
Before the Northern Guard Towers~
To the east and west of you, two great towers carved in the shape of giant
fangs rise. Several walkways encircle the towers, giving the defending drow
platforms from which to attack invaders. Most races of the underdark know
better than to attact the attention of the entire city however, and would
rather ambush patrols and lone drow than attack the city itself.  Only the
svirfneblin could pose a significant threat, and even they would be hard
pressed to fight the thousands of drow within Valshara, even in an open
field, let alone when the drow have several fortresses to which they can 
retreat.
~
