At the Gates of a Noble House~
You stand before the gates of a large noble compound. Above you guards 
scurry to and fro, attempting to determine if you approach alone or are
part of a larger force. Intrigue and subtrifuge are a way of life for the
drow, and it is often said that you must be careful not to spend too much
